<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Events</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/events.css" />
    <link
      rel="icon"
      href="https://res.cloudinary.com/dzsgjnpzh/image/upload/v1745750200/uofpduli9xgrwyu5cghb.png"
    />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.2/css/all.min.css"
      integrity="sha512-SnH5WK+bZxgPHs44uWIX+LLJAJ9/2PkPKZ5QiAj6Ta86w+fsb2TkcmfRyVX3pBnMFcV7oQPJkl9QevSCWr3W6A=="
      crossorigin="anonymous"
      referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
    />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      .activity-plan {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 4rem auto 0 auto;
        padding: 40px 30px;
      }

      .ah {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 2.8rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #003366;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      .phase {
        margin-bottom: 40px;
        padding: 30px;
        border-left: 6px solid #004080;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e6e8f0, #d0d4e2); /* Subtle gradient based on your background color */
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
      }

      .phase:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
      }

      .phase h2 {
        margin-bottom: 25px;
        color: #003366;
        font-size: 2rem;
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      .week {
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        padding-left: 20px;
        border-left: 4px solid #66a3ff;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
      }

      .week:hover {
        transform: translateX(5px);
      }

      .week h3 {
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        color: #004080;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }

      .week p {
        margin-top: 10px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: #444;
        transition: color 0.3s ease;
      }

      .week:hover p {
        color: #0052cc;
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .activity-plan {
          padding: 20px;
        }

        .ah {
          font-size: 2.4rem;
        }

        .phase h2 {
          font-size: 1.6rem;
        }

        .week h3 {
          font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include("./includes/nav.ejs") %> <%- include("./includes/cursor.ejs") %>
    <section class="activity-plan">
      <h1 class="ah">Activity Plan</h1>
      <div class="phase">
        <h2>Research and Planning (2 Weeks)</h2>

        <div class="week">
          <h3>Week 01 - 28.09.2024</h3>
          <p>
            <strong>Activity:</strong> Conduct a survey to identify the specific
            needs and challenges of rural villages regarding government schemes.
            Gather data on various government schemes relevant to farmers,
            women, healthcare, and childcare.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Activity-01:</strong> Collaborate with local government,
            NGOs, government officials, and local bodies to streamline
            collaboration for platform content and reach.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>SDG:</strong> SDG 1, 17: Partnership for the Goals, No
            Poverty
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="week">
          <h3>Week 02 - 11.10.2024</h3>
          <p>
            <strong>Activity:</strong> Analyze survey data to define the project
            scope and objectives. Prioritize which schemes will be featured on
            the platform based on the needs assessment.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="phase">
        <h2>Design & Development Preparation (2 Weeks)</h2>

        <div class="week">
          <h3>Week 03 - 26.10.2024</h3>
          <p>
            <strong>Activity:</strong> Design the structure and layout of the
            web platform, focusing on user-friendly navigation and accessibility
            for users with low digital literacy. Develop a detailed sitemap and
            wireframes for the platform.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Activity-02:</strong> Workshop with local health authorities
            on hunger programs.
          </p>
          <p><strong>SDG:</strong> SDG 2: Zero Hunger</p>
        </div>

        <div class="week">
          <h3>Week 04 - 08.11.2024</h3>
          <p>
            <strong>Activity:</strong> Promote rural education through
            initiatives like the Mid-Day Meal Scheme, Sarva Shiksha Abhiyan, and
            PMKVY to encourage regular school attendance and skill development.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="phase">
        <h2>Content Development</h2>

        <div class="week">
          <h3>Week 05 - 28.12.2024</h3>
          <p>
            <strong>Activity:</strong> Start developing the front-end of the web
            platform, ensuring it is mobile-friendly and can work on low
            bandwidth. Integrate local language support and accessibility
            features.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Activity-03:</strong> Health Conferences with NGOs and
            hospitals.
          </p>
          <p><strong>SDG:</strong> SDG 3: Good Health and Well-being</p>
        </div>

        <div class="week">
          <h3>Week 06 - 10.01.2025</h3>
          <p>
            <!-- Content for Week 06 -->
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="week">
          <h3>Week 07 - 25.01.2025</h3>
          <p>
            <strong>Activity:</strong> Complete front-end and back-end
            development with SeIntegration for Android app for easy updates.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="phase">
        <h2>Platform Building</h2>

        <div class="week">
          <h3>Week 08 - 07.02.2025</h3>
          <p>
            <strong>Activity:</strong> Develop a section for farmers, detailing
            agricultural schemes, subsidy information, crop insurance, and
            modern farming techniques.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="week">
          <h3>Week 09 - 22.02.2025</h3>
          <p>
            <strong>Activity:</strong> Encourage sustainable practices like
            organic farming through PKVY and promote renewable energy adoption.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Activity-04:</strong> Presentations to SHGs and rural
            women’s groups.
          </p>
          <p><strong>SDG:</strong> SDG 5: Gender Equality</p>
        </div>

        <div class="week">
          <h3>Week 10 - 07.03.2025</h3>
          <p>
            <strong>Activity:</strong> Develop sections for women’s empowerment
            and childcare, including self-help group schemes, maternity
            benefits, child nutrition programs, and education schemes.
          </p>
          <p>
            Ensure all content is optimized for SEO to increase visibility in
            search engines.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="week">
          <h3>Week 11 - 22.03.2025</h3>
          <p>
            <strong>Activity:</strong> Develop sections for farmers, including
            agricultural schemes and modern farming techniques.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Activity-05:</strong> Innovative Workshops/Presentations for
            rural tech solutions for the development of renewable energy for
            farming methods.
          </p>
          <p><strong>SDG:</strong> SDG 13: Climate Action</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="phase">
        <h2>Testing and Quality Assurance</h2>

        <div class="week">
          <h3>Week 12 - 29.03.2025</h3>
          <p>
            <strong>Activity:</strong> Gather feedback from a small group of
            rural users to identify usability issues and areas for improvement.
            Refine content and design based on feedback to enhance user
            experience.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Activity-06:</strong> Campaign for plastic-free village
            initiatives.
          </p>
          <p><strong>SDG:</strong> SDG 15: Life on Land</p>
        </div>

        <div class="week">
          <h3>Week 13 - 11.04.2025</h3>
          <p>
            <strong>Activity:</strong> Mid-Day Meal Scheme to address child
            malnutrition.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="phase">
        <h2>Launch Preparation</h2>

        <div class="week">
          <h3>Week 14 - 26.04.2025</h3>
          <p>
            <strong>Activity:</strong> Monitor platform performance and user
            engagement. Set up a feedback loop to continually improve the
            platform based on user needs and new government schemes.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Activity-07:</strong> Community Conference Paper for
            Sustainable Cities and Communities.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>SDG:</strong> SDG 4, 11: Quality Education, Sustainable
            Cities and Communities.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <br /><br />
    <%- include("includes/contact.ejs") %>
    <script>
      // Optional small animation for page load
      document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
        const phases = document.querySelectorAll(".phase");
        phases.forEach((phase, index) => {
          phase.style.opacity = 0;
          phase.style.transform = "translateY(50px)";
          setTimeout(() => {
            phase.style.transition = "all 0.6s ease";
            phase.style.opacity = 1;
            phase.style.transform = "translateY(0)";
          }, index * 200);
        });
      });
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
